<i>Da-dum, da-da-da, da-da-da</i>

01:17:01.659 --> 01:17:03.936
Thanks for comin'
all this way, though, man.

01:17:04.036 --> 01:17:06.079
I'm ready to leave whenever you are.

01:17:29.729 --> 01:17:31.229
What?

