I'm a connoisseur of roads.

01:35:52.163 --> 01:35:55.457
Been tasting roads my whole life.

01:35:58.545 --> 01:36:00.045
This road...

01:36:01.089 --> 01:36:03.006
will never end.

01:36:07.345 --> 01:36:09.289
It probably goes...

01:36:09.389 --> 01:36:12.349
all around...

01:36:14.018 --> 01:36:15.936
the world.

01:39:27.638 --> 01:39:31.324
<i>When I first came to London</i>

01:39:31.424 --> 01:39:34.285
<i>I was only 16</i>

01:39:34.385 --> 01:39:37.205
<i>With a fiver in my pocket</i>

01:39:37.305 --> 01:39:40.208
<i>And my old dancing bag</i>

01:39:40.308 --> 01:39:43.127
<i>I went down to the dilly</i>

01:39:43.227 --> 01:39:46.047
<i>To check out the scene</i>

01:39:46.147 --> 01:39:51.886
<i>But I soon ended up
upon the old main drag</i>

01:39:51.986 --> 01:39:54.847
<i>Where the he-males and the she-males</i>

01:39:54.947 --> 01:39:57.767
<i>Paraded in style</i>

01:39:57.867 --> 01:40:03.690
<i>And the old man with the money
would flash you a smile</i>

01:40:03.790 --> 01:40:09.529
<i>In the dark of an alley
you would work for a five</i>

01:40:09.629 --> 01:40:15.368
<i>For a swift one off the wrist
down on the old main drag</i>

01:40:15.468 --> 01:40:21.249
<i>In the cold winter nights
the old town it was chill</i>

01:40:21.349 --> 01:40:23.876
<i>But there were boys in the cafés</i>

01:40:23.976 --> 01:40:26.546
<i>Who'd give you cheap pills</i>

01:40:26.646 --> 01:40:29.424
<i>If you didn't have the money</i>

01:40:29.524 --> 01:40:32.343
<i>You'd cajole and you'd beg</i>

01:40:32.443 --> 01:40:35.346
<i>There was always lots of Tuinal</i>

01:40:35.446 --> 01:40:38.281
<i>On the old main drag</i>

01:40:49.711 --> 01:40:52.864
<i>One evening as I was lying</i>

01:40:52.964 --> 01:40:56.034
<i>Down in Leicester Square</i>

01:40:56.134 --> 01:40:58.786
<i>I was picked up by the coppers</i>

01:40:58.886 --> 01:41:01.456
<i>And kicked in the balls</i>

01:41:01.556 --> 01:41:04.667
<i>Between the metal doors at Vine Street</i>

01:41:04.767 --> 01:41:08.004
<i>I was beaten and mauled</i>

01:41:08.104 --> 01:41:10.381
<i>And they ruined my good looks</i>

01:41:10.481 --> 01:41:13.301
<i>For the old main drag</i>

01:41:13.401 --> 01:41:15.136
<i>In the tube station</i>

01:41:15.236 --> 01:41:19.182
<i>The old ones who were on the way out</i>

01:41:19.282 --> 01:41:21.893
<i>Would dribble and vomit</i>

01:41:21.993 --> 01:41:25.063
<i>And grovel and shout</i>

01:41:25.163 --> 01:41:28.441
<i>And the coppers would come along</i>

01:41:28.541 --> 01:41:30.818
<i>And push them about</i>

01:41:30.918 --> 01:41:33.905
<i>And I wished I could escape from</i>

01:41:34.005 --> 01:41:36.866
<i>The old main drag</i>

01:41:36.966 --> 01:41:39.702
<i>And now I am lying here</i>

01:41:39.802 --> 01:41:42.372
<i>I have had too much booze</i>

01:41:42.472 --> 01:41:45.333
<i>I've been spat on and shat on</i>

01:41:45.433 --> 01:41:48.795
<i>And raped and abused</i>

01:41:48.895 --> 01:41:54.050
<i>I know that I am dying
and I wish I could beg</i>

01:41:54.150 --> 01:41:59.154
<i>For some money to take me
from the old main drag</i>

01:42:45.910 --> 01:42:49.814
<i>Deep night</i>

01:42:49.914 --> 01:42:54.610
<i>Stars in the sky above</i>

01:42:54.710 --> 01:42:58.239
<i>Moonlight</i>

01:42:58.339 --> 01:43:03.286
<i>Lighting our place of love</i>

01:43:03.386 --> 01:43:06.622
<i>Night winds</i>

01:43:06.722 --> 01:43:11.502
<i>Seem to have gone to rest</i>

01:43:11.602 --> 01:43:14.797
<i>Two eyes</i>

01:43:14.897 --> 01:43:18.885
<i>Brightly with love are gleaming</i>

01:43:18.985 --> 01:43:22.847
<i>Come to my arms, my dear one</i>

01:43:22.947 --> 01:43:27.477
<i>My sweetheart, my own</i>

01:43:27.577 --> 01:43:31.481
<i>Vow that you'll love me always</i>

01:43:31.581 --> 01:43:36.694
<i>And be mine alone</i>

01:43:36.794 --> 01:43:39.989
<i>Deep night</i>

01:43:40.089 --> 01:43:44.577
<i>Whispering trees above</i>

01:43:44.677 --> 01:43:48.372
<i>Kind night</i>

01:43:48.472 --> 01:43:52.210
<i>Bringing you nearer, dearer and dearer</i>

01:43:52.310 --> 01:43:56.756
<i>Deep night</i>

01:43:56.856 --> 01:43:58.883
<i>Deep in the arms</i>

01:43:58.983 --> 01:44:03.904
<i>Of love</i>

